==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: free association
<hw>free association</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(psychoanalysis)</fld>
<def>The act or process of free-associating. It is a technique used in
psychoanalysis and is supposed to allow the analyst access to the
unconscious thoughts of the analysand. See
<er>free-associate</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Free base</ent>⟦br⟧
